Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school's pretty far away!\NWe need to get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the hold up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, Yumine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! Try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be high \Nschool students now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think your uniform\Nshould fit better than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Granny said I should get me\Na big one since I'll be growin' like a weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no provincialisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standard Japanese only!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, though. These \Nuniforms are pretty expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, I went to this school \Nfor junior high, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you went to a school out \Nin the boonies, Tama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:00:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some high hurdles to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't no hayseed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There goes your accent again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tamaki Honda, and today's\Nour high school entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshi no Tsuji Academy.\NIt's a private junior and senior high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its open atmosphere means\Nit has a lot of active clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made them pretty famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once today's ceremony is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be an event where the clubs have\Nstands and whatnot to get new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.79,0:01:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school's right in the middle of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.33,0:01:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like my junior high at all,\Nso I think it'll take some getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.25,0:01:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. We're here, Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:52.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshi no Tsuji\NJunior and Senior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,2016 Entrance Ceremony\NHoshi no Tsuji\NJunior and Senior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find it, make my day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you me for being clumsy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's a world where \Nonly love will carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left all alone like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still can't leave it be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no, it's always hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could say it was okay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could think it was okay
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange that it was just that quick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of chasing this kind of thrill
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:03:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will be more than you could \Nhave imagined yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, make my day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic that we all hold
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see the greatest \Nsomething of your life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find it, make my day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you me for being clumsy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a world waiting where \Nonly love will carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Starting Line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done with the ceremony and homeroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so now it's time to check \Nout the clubs' PR event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've waited so long for this day,\Nto join up with a nice club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:49.71,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance | Club | Table Tennis | Volleyball
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for something \Nthat'll really draw me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know what that is yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first PR event, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the new blood is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had a shift with\Nthe Desktop Music Club, Fujikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah. But this is important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping we get a good artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An aspiring voice actor would be nice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll be that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me. Mind wearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the club captain wears that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. And starting \Ntoday, the captain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done. We need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break a leg, Ms. New Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Tea\NCeremony\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of clubs here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've seen more,\Nbut it's getting a bit late...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Starting a new club\Nhere is so very easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This green tea is something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:06.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Track Team
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, found a good club yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many,\Nand I have to talk with all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my. Well, I joined the Illustration Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't know they had one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about what\Nkind of club you want to join?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find something that grabs me\Nlike it's my divine calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to worry about.\NYou'll find something for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:38.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SNS\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've got all sorts of clubs, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smiles of youth are so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Shii!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll reflect on why\NI kept you up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:49.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SNS\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, what kind of club is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our club makes doujin games.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can even play something we've made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Doujin" means fan-made media.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make games yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a doujin game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing fancy, but we have\Na promo video for it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The computer froze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll restart it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tea! It's gonna get on the computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a puzzle game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The graphics are so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.88,0:06:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach's doing flips.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, guess I need to pick a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can start first, Tama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yumine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just got inspiration \Nfor my next script!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:46.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bwehehehe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try smiling a little less creepily, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already throwing bad guys at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's giving us control cues!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the tutorial is any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried hard to get all the bugs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a real trick to \Nmoving the balls around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty cerebral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my little kittens,\Nbecome enamored with my story!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a puzzle game, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart was pumping like crazy,\Nbut it sure was a rush when it disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they cute... Nothing \Nquite like newbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't what you were \Nsaying before, Shii...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, we ran out of time. \NWe almost had it cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for getting all excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. That's what makes it all worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you sure put your \Nhearts and souls into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe a club made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! I got a game called Hoyofuyo once\Nand it was just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded me of how into it I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your inspiration for this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We based it on rules that are\Npretty common for action puzzle games,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was bound to show \Nup in there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I kind of knew what I was doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shii! Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I say something wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And both of you made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Made it we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got two more people \Non our team, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check out the jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do you make them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do the artwork, scripts,\Nand music on the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,A young man is washing himself\Nin the river one day when a boss\Ncomes from upstream!\NFrom the river, a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we start putting them together\Ninto a proper game format.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we all come together to\Nmake the world of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you use computers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to draw, but I haven't \Ndone much digital stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, you just have to \Nease yourself into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I don't think \NI can join your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably going to be busy\Nwith the Illustration Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Tama-chan?\NI remember how much you liked to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little back in elementary school, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about\Ndrawing with computers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't think I could\Nmake stuff for a game like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that big a deal, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she look so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thanks for stopping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Basketball Team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those new students were so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it's over already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just join \Nthe Tea Ceremony Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain was such a sweetheart...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could join\Nthe Illustration Club with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sat in with them and it seemed really relaxed.\NI think it might be a nice place to draw in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That game sure was fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sparkly and cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all super serious about making games.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck do I want to do, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:08.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Junior High Third Year\NCard Games
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get really into card games and\Nstudy a lot about single player games...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:12.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Junior High Second Year\NReading
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit on the riverbank watching the clouds\Nand blowing through the classics...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Junior High First Year\NTracing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spend pretty much all \Nmy time copying manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary Fifth Year\NManga
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go into the closet and get \Nlost in a nice manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:24.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary Third Year\NDoodling
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See how good I could \Ndoodle in my textbooks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary First Year\NBug Catching
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch bugs and study them on my porch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I just stick to a hobby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:38.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SUPER SUGOROKU\NGOAL\NPrize:\N1,000,000 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make yourself a board game today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're something else when it comes to\Nmaking games, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm an elementary schooler,\Nme and my friends are gonna play lots of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of games for a sweetie pie like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Yumine and I got to be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a new game for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Hey," Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking of games...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yumine! You can go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama-chan!\NSorry, Yumine! You can go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that a first year?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Fujikawa.\NI'm a second year with the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That and the sound director\Nfor this puzzle game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get to play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The music...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was just so into \Nthe game I didn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I guess I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Background music doesn't exactly stick out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:12:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like there're many people who'd notice\Nhow much work somebody put into a bass line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! I didn't mean it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm pulling your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a game where nothing sticks out\Nmeans the sound person's done their job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why'd you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I really liked the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it got me interested in making games...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'd be a good artist,\Nbut maybe the person who did it could teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then maybe I could do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She put this club together a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She pulled us in and this puzzle game\Nwas our debut project.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did the art, the planning,\Nand managed it all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then she graduated.\NSo that left the three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without an artist or\Nanyone who wanted to be a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're kind of up the creek here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you don't have an artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought maybe one of the\Nnew students could be one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't get a single new member...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the first day of the new semester!\NThe game hasn't even started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your new member!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Please and thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I promise I'll learn \Nhow to use a computer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That means so much! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you draw?\NHave you done illustrations before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've traced manga before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I'd like to try\Nmaking a game if you'd let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're more than welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you draw something now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what she draws!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't sketched for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. Well I think it's pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.17,0:14:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tamaki Honda, and \NI'm going to make games!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you ended up joining\Nthe game club, Tama-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. They didn't have anyone who could draw,\Nso I thought maybe they could take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're already meeting up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they get up to\Nat a game making meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the \NIllustrator's Club, Yumine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we have to do introductions today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get nervous when you\Nshow your art to other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of the art seniors got his tea drunk\Nby this kinda cute guy next to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he looked super embarrassed about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day has come at last, Shii!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how long our club has waited for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the semester's just started, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They put a new flavor on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice little bit of chaos,\Nthe mixing of these two mundane flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:02.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Matcha Tea\NPudding\NLemonade
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such simple stimuli that free us\Nfrom the humdrum, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Could you just drink it, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SNS\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, newbie! How about \Nyou introduce yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, newbie!\NWe're glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tamaki Honda and I'm a first year!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a lot to learn about making\Ngames and art, but I'm glad to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I brought this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny said I ought to greet people properly\Nwhen I get to my new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...\NWell, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so flavorful. That's some good kinpira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Kinpira is a dish generally made out\N of chopped burdock and carrot sautéed\N in soy sauce and sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good and all, but is this\Nwhat our club should be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain's up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shiina Murakami, second year.\NI'm our programmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to meet you, Ms. Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I just barged into the club-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That kind of energy is great\Nwhen you're making something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well when I saw how serious you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it really made me think how much\NI wanted to make games with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how I looked?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I was thinking of
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how best to punish a certain script writer\Nwho'd gone crazy the previous night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call in the dead of night telling me\Nhow we need to add a secret boss to our demo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just thought it \Nmight not be hard enough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for any veteran players who\Nstopped by our club for the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job being only to adjust the values of the AI,\NI figured we'd be able to manage something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet the one who proposed\Nthis idea in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,decided she wanted to play another game...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That wasn't just playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be good \Nto study a classic RPG!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might want to \Nstay on her good side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when did you get to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the script supervisor,\Nsecond year Ayame Seki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a second year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Background music and\NSFX director Kayo Fujikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, you all can do such amazing stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this club, the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slack-eyed Night-owl \NShuttle-runners Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slack-eyed Night-owl \NShuttle-runners Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not exactly a story \Nyou can tell in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, about where we go from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, we managed to make a single puzzle game
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the behest of our founder and senior member.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But being that she's no longer here,\Nand us being amateurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be best to start with\Na small plan and step up from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've cooked up a new \Nscenario just for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider me the leader of\Nthe SNS Club's second project!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:17:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you can handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm feeling kind of hurt, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You want to do a \Nspin-off of the puzzle game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-exactly. I thought we could do\Na short, simple visual novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I could make the music arrangements\Nout of stuff from the old game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't this so exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll be doing the art, Honda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to use a computer... won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it doesn't work \Nout, it doesn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Character poses and variations, \NUI design, stills...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in charge of making all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, because this is a group project,\Nyou'll have deadlines to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you could ease up \Non the pressure, Murakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to force anyone into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a game is hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. It's probably \Ngoing to be hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even picture what it's like to make\Nart for a game, so maybe I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to spend any \Nmore time without a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make the games I can make!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that, Honda-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:25.88,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Our New Plan\N- Deadlines\N- Volume\N- Scheduling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go over our schedule once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, while we have any number of\Ndoujin fairs to choose from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be aiming for Summer Comiket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Summer Comiket"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really large doujin event\Nheld during summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our goal is to join it \Nwith our newly finished game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be flirting with disaster \Nwith such a hard schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the game you made!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't have to \Nbase the art off of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we want is a game \Nwith your personal touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably try to get \Na song done by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:20:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...? You can make music that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should do something, too-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down! You're making me feel pressured!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think you could've gone a \Nlittle easier on her, Shii?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-san's probably going to\Nhave a lot more work to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she can't keep up and \Nends up keeling over...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. But let's keep \Nour eyes on the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you that \Nexcited in a long time, Shii.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because we've never had\Na junior member before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be failures and setbacks along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can get there with the four of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be hard at work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider this a thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to keep that to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:11.79,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,New Game\NContinue\NOptions\NHelp
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up drawing at this hour, Tamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut off that TV and get some sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this looks pretty good for a copy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What we want is a game \Nwith your personal touch."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know what I want to do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they reached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Longing gazes, standing on tiptoes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Washed away, reeling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swimming through a sea of dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.67,0:22:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lullaby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:23:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swaying
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, the evening dew upon the leontochir!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop with the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe there's \Nsome room for an older man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing with a face like that, I figured that\Nour characters would look all happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who drew \Nthe pictures, Tama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:36.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fun Production
